args: I am beautiful. I am BEAUTIFUL!\nI...AM...BEAUTIFUUUUUUL!
Gya! Every single morning, you start\nrunnin' your mouth as soon as the cock\ncrows! It is SO irritating!
I'm gonna shut you and that weird voice\nof yours up for good. Get ready for pain!
You're in my way, child. Move!
Every single morning... I'm so sick of it!
I ain't gonna be satisfied until I give that\nguy a whack on the head that leaves him\nspinning in his...er...not-grave.
Oh, skin! My skin is so pretty!\nThat's why I sing this lovely little ditty!
Now he's singing and washing his face like\nI ACTUALLY GIVE A CRAP!
HEY! Zardin! I got somethin' to say to you,\nbuddy, so listen up!
So sorry! Can't listen right now.\nMust practice proper skin hydration.\n*dab* *dab* *dab*
...The heck are you putting on your face,\nweirdo? Is this some occult ceremony?\nBecause I am OUT if so.
Ceremony? Heavens, no. I'm merely\napplying my special cleansing gel\nthat hydrates and revitalizes the pores.
Here, you should try it. It's ever so\nrefreshing. *dab* *dab* *dab*
Gyaaa! Get that stuff off my face!
Nice and gentle, round and round...\nAnd after we massage it in, we rinse with\nrefreshing cool water. *splash* *sploosh*
What the hell is happening right now?
Start by getting your face nice and clean;\nWe'll talk more after that. Aha ha ha!
Hey! ...Dammit, he ran off again.\nNow I gotta do something about\nall this crap he put on my face...
Right then! Walking! One, two, and turn!\nChest, puffed! Back, straight! Aaand...\nBEAUTY POSE!
Ah ha! THERE he is! ...Okay, he HAS to be\nin the middle of some awful ceremony\nthis time.
...Ack! There's a fiend in front of him!
Do not interfere with my beautiful walking,\nyou churl!
Phew! And with that, all the bumps\nalong my road to beauty have been\neliminated.

Now then, if I remember correctly,
{player_name} asked that I come
along as his comrade on a
fiend-slaying expedition today.
Will I keep walking like this as I make\nmy way to him? I will! Aaaand...STRUT!
You know, I hate to admit this, but his\npassion for perfecting his beauty is\nalmost...impressive.
Anyway, guess I'll withdraw for now.
Although...hmmm. I wonder if there's\nsome significance to the way Zardin\nwas sauntering about just now.
It was like...this? Walking, one, two?
Nice work on the fiend-slaying, Prince.
Thanks, Johanna. Um, you're looking\nkind of...lustrous today.
Ya know, I was thinkin' the same thing.\nStandin' a little taller than usual, too.
You been gettin' up earlier lately, yeah?\nThat got somethin' to do with it?
Aha! Aha ha ha! But of course!
Because the reason Johanna has become\nso radiant is...me! Zardin!
Early to rise and early to bed...\nTaking meticulous care of the skin...\nModerate exercise and gorgeous posture...
She emulated mein all my beautyto\nperfection, and thus it was inevitable that\nshe, too, became beautiful!
Wait a sec... DID I do that?
(Hmm... His terrible singing and ungodly\nscreaming did cause to me start going\nto bed earlier...)
(And I did that skin-care thing today...\nPlus I got exercise chasing him around...\nOh my gosh. Is he RIGHT?!)
Well, regardless of how, it's great.\nHell, yer gonna be prettier than\nZardin before long!
I think you're just a natural at this beauty\nstuff, Johanna.
Someone more beautiful than I? Absurd!\nPreposterous! Completely without merit!\nI will forever be the most beautiful!
Wait, weren't ya proud of her until, like,\ntwo seconds ago?
He's just poutin' now, Johanna.\nBe nice to him.
Why is that suddenly MY problem?!
*sigh* Look, stop it already. We all know\nyou care about beauty more than anyone.
AHA HA HA! I KNEW IT! Iand only I\nam number one! My beauty is the most\nbeauteous of them all!
That doesn't mean you can be annoying\nabout it. Knock it off already!
So does that mean being on good terms\nwith someone also counts as beauty?
Heh. Couldnt've said it better myself.
